<%= render 'shared/header', title: 'About Us' %>
<section class="wrapper !bg-[#ffffff]">
  <div class="container pt-20 xl:pt-18 lg:pt-18 md:pt-18 pb-16 xl:pb-20 lg:pb-20 md:pb-20">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-15px] xl:mx-[-35px] lg:mx-[-20px] mt-[-50px] items-center">
      <!-- Tekst sekcija -->
      <div class="w-full xl:w-12/12 lg:w-12/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full mt-[50px] !relative">
        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle1.svg", class: "h-9 !absolute xl:block lg:block", style: "top: -5%; left: -2%", alt: "doodle") %>
        <h2 class="text-[calc(1.305rem_+_0.66vw)] font-bold xl:text-[1.8rem] leading-[1.3] !mb-3">
          A Team That Works Differently
        </h2>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">We’re not just another agency churning out mass emails and generic campaigns. We are a small, highly skilled team working with a select number of businesses that value quality over quantity. Our approach is not about automation or shortcuts - it’s about building real connections, managing conversations with care, and ensuring every outreach effort is backed by thorough research and a clear strategy.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">We specialise in B2B lead generation, demand generation, LinkedIn and email outreach, and appointment setting - but not in the way most companies do it. Instead of blasting messages to thousands and hoping for a response, we take a structured, hands-on approach. Every company we work with gets the attention it deserves because we see ourselves as an extension of your business. Our team dives deep into understanding your market, refining your messaging, and making sure that the right conversations happen with the right people at the right time.</p>
        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle4.svg", class: "h-8 !absolute xl:block lg:block !rounded-[.4rem]", style: "bottom: -3%; right: 1%", alt: "doodle") %>
      </div>
      <!-- /.row -->
    </div>
    <!--/column -->
  </div>
  <!--/.row -->
</div>
<!-- /.container -->
</section>
