        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle1.svg", class: "h-9 !absolute xl:block lg:block", style: "top: -5%; left: -2%", alt: "doodle") %>
        <h2 class="text-[calc(1.305rem_+_0.66vw)] font-bold xl:text-[1.8rem] leading-[1.3] !mb-3">
          Who We Are (Without the Names)
        </h2>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">Our team consists of experienced sales professionals, account managers, intercultural communication specialists, marketing strategists, designers, and PR experts. Each of us brings a unique skill set, but we all share the same goal - helping your business find and connect with the right partners, clients, and opportunities.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">You won’t find a list of names or job titles here, and that’s intentional. We’re not in this for personal recognition, and we don’t believe a list of fancy job titles tells you much about what we actually do. What matters is the work, the process, and the results we deliver. Every client who works with us meets the full team within the first few weeks. You’ll know exactly who’s handling your outreach, who’s managing your campaigns, and who’s making sure everything runs smoothly.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">We don’t hide behind a logo, either. We’re real people, and our clients know that. We’re in constant communication, fine-tuning our strategies, adjusting our outreach, and making sure your business is getting in front of the right audience in a way that makes sense for your industry and goals.</p>
        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle4.svg", class: "h-8 !absolute xl:block lg:block !rounded-[.4rem]", style: "bottom: -3%; right: 1%", alt: "doodle") %>
      </div>
      <!-- /.row -->
    </div>
    <!--/column -->
  </div>
  <!--/.row -->
</div>
<!-- /.container -->
</section>
<section class="wrapper !bg-[#ffffff]">
  <div class="container pt-20 xl:pt-18 lg:pt-18 md:pt-18 pb-16 xl:pb-20 lg:pb-20 md:pb-20">
