      <div class="w-full xl:w-12/12 lg:w-12/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full mt-[50px] !relative">
        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle1.svg", class: "h-9 !absolute xl:block lg:block", style: "top: -5%; left: -2%", alt: "doodle") %>
        <h2 class="text-[calc(1.305rem_+_0.66vw)] font-bold xl:text-[1.8rem] leading-[1.3] !mb-3">
          Why We Work With a Limited Number of Companies
        </h2>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">Unlike large agencies that take on hundreds of clients at once, we deliberately keep our client base small. That’s because we believe in commitment and quality. Every company we work with receives direct attention from our team - there’s no outsourcing, no passing work down a chain of junior employees, and no ‘set it and forget it’ approach.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">We take the time to understand your business inside and out. That means learning about your market, your competitors, your ideal customers, and the challenges you face. It means testing different approaches, refining messaging, and adapting based on real-time data. It means making sure that every single outreach effort is aligned with your business goals, rather than just sending messages for the sake of activity.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">We believe in meaningful growth, and that’s only possible when the right people are having the right conversations. That’s what we do. We don’t take on just anyone, and we don’t work with companies that don’t align with our values. If we work together, it’s because we see real potential to help you grow in a way that makes sense.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">MOO is not just a service - it’s a partnership. If you want mass outreach with no real strategy, we’re not for you. But if you want a team that actually cares about your success, then you’re in the right place.</p>
        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle4.svg", class: "h-8 !absolute xl:block lg:block !rounded-[.4rem]", style: "bottom: -3%; right: 1%", alt: "doodle") %>
      </div>
      <!-- /.row -->
    </div>
    <!--/column -->
  </div>
  <!--/.row -->
</div>
<!-- /.container -->
</section>